for the 100% MR golems they had 7 pets tanking, plus the clerics had SS leggings; make sure they have that before you got up there to try it!, just stood there click click cliking away.  From what my friend said they took down just about every mob on the first floor in record timing and got very good exp, too bad they didn't hvae any warriors or bards to loot.  I will say this, the pally walked away with a near Full Set of Valorium hehe.  Now personally I would rather use a bard to a pally for running song, but I don't think it matters if they can run fast enough.   But he careful if you do try this.  one wrong move can get you killed.  The reason they used a pally was for LoH I think, but monk or bard would probably be better since they can run faster, and at 60 bards get that invincibility song hehe.  I would like to hear some info from you guys, the hard part will be finding enough mage's with Scint to actually do the dmg needed hehe.<br>
